OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782505102
OL,3,CMan bitten by 'pitbull-type' dog in
OL,4,CMiddlesbrough park
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for information
OL,7,Fafter a man was bitten by a 'pitbull
OL,8,Ftype' dog in Middlesbrough.
OL,10,FIt happened at around 11.50pm on
OL,11,FWednesday 24 June when the man was
OL,12,Fwalking alone in Pallister Park.
OL,14,FThe dog - which was without its owner
OL,15,F- ran towards him and bit him on the
OL,16,Farm.
OL,18,FHe was dragged to the ground and
OL,19,Frepeatedly bitten before the dog ran
OL,20,Foff in an unknown direction.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
