CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782505102
OL,3,CMan bitten by 'pitbull-type' dog in
OL,4,CMiddlesbrough park
OL,6,FThe man was found lying on the ground
OL,7,Fby a member of the public nearby and
OL,8,Fan ambulance was called.
OL,10,FInvestigating officer, PC Davison,
OL,11,Fsaid: "Since the report was made, we
OL,12,Fhave started making enquiries in a bid
OL,13,Fto identify the owner and locate the
OL,14,Fdog.
OL,16,F"At this stage we are unsure of the
OL,17,Fwhereabouts of the dog and would
OL,18,Fencourage anyone resides in the area
OL,19,Fand may know who the owner is to get
OL,20,Fin touch.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782505102
OL,3,CMan bitten by 'pitbull-type' dog in
OL,4,CMiddlesbrough park
OL,6,F"I would also ask anyone who has seen
OL,7,Fthe dog to get in touch with us."
OL,9,FAnyone with information is urged to
OL,10,Fcall 101, or to visit Cleveland
OL,11,FPolice's website quoting reference
OL,12,Fnumber 123931.
OL,14,FInformation can also be provided
OL,15,Fanonymously by calling Crimestoppers
OL,16,Fon 0800 555 111.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/3
